{"tid":2427494,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"南韓累計逾2萬人接種疫苗　112人出現一般不良反應","createTime":"2021-02-28T23:38:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T00:21:23.000Z","uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c7ac5ddb32a4915215dbc6ae883c4c55526e9f86","tid":2427494,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T23:38:21.000Z","msg":"南韓累計逾2萬人接種疫苗　112人出現一般不良反應<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1577996-20210228.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1577996-20210228.htm&d=FWesCxf%2Fx1R8NKF8yEGh3SK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=40f67fb7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1577996-20210228.htm&h=77591b23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1577996-20210228.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n南韓前日展開新型冠狀病毒疫苗接種工作，累計有超過2萬人接種。防疫部門表示，前日和昨日共收到112宗接種疫苗後出現異常反應的報告，都屬於一般不良反應，包括發燒、頭痛、噁心及嘔吐等。<br />\n<br />\n當局表示，兩天內收到的112宗異常反應報告，111宗與阿斯利康疫苗有關，1宗與輝瑞疫苗有關。"},{"pid":"bb327e0e87aecdd33fe09c9299dda865df61ebe5","tid":2427494,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T00:16:02.000Z","msg":"Biontech輝瑞？"},{"pid":"17479bfa3d478ba1e25c9347f11dd0afb00a431c","tid":2427494,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T00:19:52.000Z","msg":"咁pfizer 真係好safe<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2eee7b35bcd1e118bf22b48963c81ce37585b06","tid":2427494,"uid":56957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T00:21:23.000Z","msg":"即係1%不良反應都無"}]}